Ing '''Santa Sede''' o '''Banal a Sede''' ({{lang-lat|Sancta Sedes}}, {{lang-it|Santa Sede}}), ({{lang-en|Holy See}}),  ing awtoridad a episkopal ning Pisambang Katoliku o Iglesia Catolica king [[Roma]]. Uli ning pamibabo o pamanimuna (''primacy'') ning Roma, ing kayang obispu ning pekapun ning pangyatung pisamban o iglesia, at iti keraklan mayayaus yang [[Papa]] (''Pope''). Uling ing Roma ing pekamatas nang sedeng episkopal o tungkung pang-obispu ning Pisamban o Iglesia, iti ing karinan ning kapamahalang sentral o pangkalibudtan ning pisamban, kayabe no deng miyayaliwang ahensyang kaylangan king pamanibala. King diplomasya, ing Sante Sede ing kikimut ampong magsalita para king mabilug a Pisambang Katolika o Iglesia Catolica. Kikilalanan de mu naman deng aliwang sakup ning leying internasyunal o ''international law'' antimong bageng magsarili o soberanung karinan, a panibalan ning Papa, at malyaring mika ugnayang diplomatiku (''diplomatic relations'') kaniti.<ref>Text taken directly from http://www.fco.gov.uk/en/travel-and-living-abroad/travel-advice-by-country/country-profile/europe/holy-see/ (viewed on 14 December 2011), on the website of the British Foreign & Commonwealth Office.</ref><ref>Makikilala ya ing soberania na ning Santa Sede kareng dakal a pamikasundung internasyunal, at partikular mititimid ya king artikulo 2 of the [[Tratadung Lateranu]] (''Lateran Treaty'') ]] ning 11 Febrero 1929, nung nu "Kikilalanan ning Italia ing soberania na ning Santa Sede king larangan a internasyunal antimong kakabit o kayanib ning kayang naturalesa, agpang king tradisyun, ampo reng pamangaylangan ning kayang misyon king yatu." ("Italy recognizes the sovereignty of the Holy See in the international field as an inherent attribute of its nature, in conformity with its tradition, and the requirements of its mission in the world.")</ref>

Maralas, mayayaus ya iting "ing Vaticano", dapot e pareung bage ing Santa Sede king Estadung [[Vatican Lakabalen]], a linto mu anyang  
1929; ing Santa Sede, ing diosesis o sede episkopal ning Roma, manibat ya pa kanitang mumuna nang dake ning panaung Cristiano. Deng embahador makadestinu la e king Estadung Vatican Lakanbalen (''Vatican City State''), nun e king "Santa Sede", (''"the Holy See"), at deng pekakatawan ning papa kikilalanan da lang pekakatawan ning Santa Sede, at e ning Estadung Vatican Lakanbalen.

Lipat ning mituturing la ngang "holy" ("holy") deng anggang diosesis o [[sede episkopal]], ing terminung "Santa Sede" (a ala nang kayabe) normal yang magagamit king ugnayang internasyunal ampo king leying canon ning Pisambang Katoliku o Iglesia Catolica.  
 <ref>[http://www.intratext.com/IXT/ENG0017/_P19.HTM Code of Canon Law, canon 361], [http://www.intratext.com/IXT/LAT0758/_P7.HTM Code of Canons of the Eastern Churches, canon 48]</ref> to refer to the See of Rome viewed as the central government of the Roman Catholic Church.

